      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a superlative E46 M3, a definitive example of the high-revving S54 platform. This chassis features the iconic 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six independent throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously serviced for optimal timing and torque delivery. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock, ensuring exceptional power distribution. Critically, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to mitigate structural fatigue, and the suspension retains its factory-spec kinematics with fresh bushings and dampers. The aesthetic condition is concours-level, with no paint oxidation or interior leather bolstering wear. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the enthusiast who demands peak longitudinal and lateral performance without compromise.",
